import React, { Fragment } from "react";
import { Form, FormGroup } from "reactstrap";

const AddEmployee= () =>{
    return(
        <Fragment>
            <Form>
                <FormGroup>
                    <label for="exampleEmployeeNo">Employee No</label>
                        <input type="text" name="empNo" id="empNo" placeholder="Employee No" />
                </FormGroup>
                <FormGroup>
                    <label for="exampleEmployeeName">Employee Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="empNm" id="empNm" placeholder="Employee Name" />
                </FormGroup>
                <FormGroup>
                    <label for="exampleDoj">Date Of Joing</label>
                        <input type="Date" name="empDOJ" id="empDOJ" placeholder="Date Of Joining" />
                </FormGroup>
                <FormGroup>
                    <label for="exampleDept">Department</label>
                    <input type="select" name="select" id="exampleSelect">
                            <option value="AD">Administration</option>
                            <option value="IT">Inforamtion Technology</option>
                            <option value="HD">Help Desk</option>
                            <option value="HR">Human Resource</option>
                            <option value="OP">Operation</option>
                    </input>
                </FormGroup>
                <FormGroup>
                    <label for="exampleSalary">Salary</label>
                        <input type="text" name="salary" id="salary" placeholder="Salary" />
                </FormGroup>
            </Form>
        </Fragment>
    );
};

export default AddEmployee;
